A view of the Torrance Refining Company facility, opened in 1929. A hundred years ago Torrance was a <a href="https://www.torranceca.gov/our-city/about-torrance/1930s" target="_blank">center of oil production</a>, and while most of the oil wells are gone today, several oil refineries still operate in the area.


 </p>


 <p class="jp">    
 <span class="title_jp">トルランス製油所</span>

 1929年に開業したトルランス製油所の様子。100年前、トルランスは石油生産の拠点であり、現在ではほとんどの油井が廃止されたものの、地域内には複数の製油所が操業を続けています。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Torrance" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A view of the Torrance Refining Company facility, opened in 1929. A hundred years ago Torrance was a center of oil production, and while most of the oil wells are gone today, several oil refineries still operate in the area.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R08493_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R08493_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Culver Blvd. Street Scene</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250812/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Culver Blvd. Street Scene" /><published>2025-08-12T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2025-08-12T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/culver-blvd</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250812/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
A long exposure captures the cars, lights, and people enjoying a summer evening in central Culver City.
 </p>


 <p class="jp">    
 <span class="title_jp">カルバー・ブールバードの街並み</span>
長時間露光により、カルバーシティ中心部の夏の夜を楽しむ車や明かり、人々の様子を捉えています。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Southern California" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Street" /><category term="Long Exposure" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A long exposure captures the cars, lights, and people enjoying a summer evening in central Culver City.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R08461_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R08461_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Culver City Stairs</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250811/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Culver City Stairs" /><published>2025-08-11T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2025-08-11T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/culver-city-stairs</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250811/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
After walking up the stairs at the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Baldwin_Hills_Scenic_Overlook_State_Park" target="_blank">Baldwin Hills Scenic Overlook</a>, visitors take in the view of Century City and West Los Angeles in the afternoon fog.
 </p>


 <p class="jp">    
 <span class="title_jp">カルバー・シティ・ステアーズ</span>
ボールドウィン・ヒルズ・シーニック・オーバーロックの階段を登った後、訪問者は午後の霧に包まれたセンチュリーシティとウェストロサンゼルスの景色を眺めることができます。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Southern California" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[After walking up the stairs at the Baldwin Hills Scenic Overlook, visitors take in the view of Century City and West Los Angeles in the afternoon fog.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R08407_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R08407_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Catalina in the Clouds</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250810/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Catalina in the Clouds" /><published>2025-08-10T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2025-08-10T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/catalina</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250810/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Looking south towards Catalina Island at sunset from the Palos Verdes Peninsula, while the ocean is covered in low lying clouds.
 </p>


   <p class="jp"> 
       <span class="title_jp">雲の中のカタリナ島</span>
 パロスバーデス半島から、夕暮れのカタリナ島を南に望む。海は低い雲に覆われている。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><category term="Fog" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking south towards Catalina Island at sunset from the Palos Verdes Peninsula, while the ocean is covered in low lying clouds.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R08352_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R08352_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Helms Bakery</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250809/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Helms Bakery" /><published>2025-08-09T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2025-08-09T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/helms-bakery</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250809/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Art deco façade of a portion of the Helms Bakery building (1931), brought into sharp relief by  Southern California’s morning sunlight.
 </p>


   <p class="jp">    
ヘルムズ・ベーカリービル（1931年）の一部にあるアールデコ様式のファサードが、南カリフォルニアの朝の陽光によって鮮明に浮かび上がっています。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Southern California" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Art deco façade of a portion of the Helms Bakery building (1931), brought into sharp relief by Southern California’s morning sunlight.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_DSCF1211.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_DSCF1211.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Beach Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250806/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Beach Sunset" /><published>2025-08-06T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2025-08-06T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/16th-st</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250806/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Sun sets into the Pacific Ocean, at 16th St. in Hermosa Beach. </p>
<p class="en">
There was a time I would post photos like this almost every day.  But that is in the past.
</p>

   <p class="jp">    
<span class="title_jp">ビーチ・サンセット</span>
夕日がブラフ・コーブの上の崖を黄金色に照らす。
太平洋に沈む夕日、ハーモサ・ビーチの16th St.にて。
</p>

<p class="jp">    
ほぼ毎日、こんな写真を投稿していた時期もあった。しかし過去のものとなった。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Sun sets into the Pacific Ocean, at 16th St. in Hermosa Beach. There was a time I would post photos like this almost every day. But that is in the past.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R08300_ai-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R08300_ai-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Soap Bubbles</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250802/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Soap Bubbles" /><published>2025-08-02T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2025-08-02T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/bubbles</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250802/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
